\b\fs36 \cf2 How to use:
\b0\fs24 \cf0 \
\
Select a playlist--or select a single track in a playlist--and launch the applet by selecting it from the iTunes Script menu. This dialog will appear:\
\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\li180\ri-2162\pardirnatural
